        dd
          p.
            AI-powered tools like Co-Pilot shine when they combine intelligence with purpose.
            Workflows and Adaptive Cards allow these systems to:
          ul
            li Guide users through complex tasks with step-by-step instructions.
            li Present relevant, actionable information without overwhelming the user.
            li Adjust dynamically to user input while staying aligned with the overall objective.

        dt Meeting System Requirements with Adaptive Workflows
        dd
          p.
            One of the challenges of integrating AI into chat applications is ensuring compliance with system requirements. Workflow-driven design provides the control and flexibility needed to:
          ul
            li Enforce business rules and compliance standards.
